
      <section class="section__customerservice-faq">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="customer-service-card">
            <div class="customer-service-card-image">
              <img src="/images/faqs-image.webp" alt="Man training in gym" />
            </div>

            <div class="customer-service-card__content customer-service-card__content--faq">
              <span class="ui-badge">Frequently Asked Questions</span>

              <h2>Common questions about gym and training</h2>

              <div class="faq-accordion">
                <details open class="faq-item">
                  <summary>
                    <span class="faq-question"
                      >Q1. Do I need prior gym experience to join
                      CoreFitness?</span
                    >
                    <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="faq-item__content">
                    <p>
                      No. Our memberships are built for all fitness levels, and
                      our trainers can help you get started with a safe plan and
                      proper technique.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>Intro session available for new members</li>
                      <li>Beginner-friendly programs that scale with you</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>
                    <span class="faq-question"
                      >Q2. What facilities are included with the
                      membership?</span
                    >
                    <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="faq-item__content">
                    <p>
                      Access varies by membership tier, but typically includes
                      gym equipment, changing rooms, and selected group classes.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>
                    <span class="faq-question"
                      >Q3. Can I try the gym before taking a membership?</span
                    >
                    <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="faq-item__content">
                    <p>
                      Yes. Contact us and we’ll help you book a trial visit so
                      you can see the facilities and meet the team.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>
                    <span class="faq-question"
                      >Q4. Are there group workout programs available?</span
                    >
                    <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="faq-item__content">
                    <p>
                      Yes. We offer group training options at different levels,
                      depending on your location and schedule.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>
                    <span class="faq-question"
                      >Q5. Is nutrition guidance included in the plans?</span
                    >
                    <span class="faq-toggle" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="faq-item__content">
                    <p>
                      Some plans include nutrition support. If it’s not
                      included, we can recommend add-ons or coaching options.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </details>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>